{"title":"红河素描（二首）","authors":["周纲"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河素描（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗衣曲中越农家女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下河去洗衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗呀洗呀洗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依荡涟漪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头相对望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陌生又熟悉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晚常相见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗衣又淘米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔河话不通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声传情意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你唱劳动党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我唱毛主席……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话语虽不懂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿当翻译。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情和厚意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒在红河里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多白的衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多纯的友谊……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中越桥头过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两国的边地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插着一杆旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河桥是一座轿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬着虚胖的殖民者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴黎的香槟酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿着谁的泪滴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血的山洪暴发了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪的洪水冲倒忍耐的堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暴的巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撕下耻辱的标记！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像摘下一片枯叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让红河的浪头卷去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳陪红旗冉冉升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天春风吻着两国红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红河桥伸开铁臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽住两个战斗的兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把一颗心掷下红河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为风云变色的海洋带去……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}